					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">TXA does the opposite of what you want to do. You want to move A (calculated index into bit mask table) into X, so you need TAX. And you want to treat all bits other than the selected bit as if they're 0, so you need AND instead of ORA.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

