						<div class="postbody">To clear bit 0:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">lda value<br />and #%11111110<br />sta value<br /></div><br /><br />To clear bit 1:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">lda value<br />and #%11111101<br />sta value<br /></div><br /><br />To clear bit 2:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">lda value<br />and #%11111011<br />sta value<br /></div><br /><br />See the pattern yet?</div>

